'''Moxie''' is a Battle [[Key Words|key word]] for [[Smith]].

==Effect==
In game description: "Whenever you take damage on your turn, increase your '''Moxie''' by a random amount between 1 and 2.

At the end of your turn, [[Heal]] health equal to your '''Moxie''' and then halve your '''Moxie''' down to a minimum of 1".

